##############################################
This code creates EC2-Ubuntu instances. After the creation of instance nginx is installed on those instances.

Steps to run the code to create infrastructure:
1. terraform init - It downloads the aws provider for Terraform.
2. terraform plan - To preview the infrastructure being created.
3. terraform apply - To create the infrastructure.


########### To run code using Jenkins ###################

Steps:
1. Install Jenkins on the server.
2. Install terraform plugin in Jenkins. ( Manage Jenkins > Manage Plugins > Available > Terraform )
3. Configure Terraform in Global tool configuration.
4. Create new Jenkins pipeline, use pipeline script using scm, provide git url and Jenkinsfile path.
5. Trigger the build.
